9
00:00:20,477 --> 00:00:22,443
To celebrate my first paycheck,

10
00:00:22,443 --> 00:00:24,643
I got you a little something.

11
00:00:24,643 --> 00:00:27,210
Summer, you're the best!

12
00:00:27,543 --> 00:00:29,010
Open it and see if you like it.

13
00:00:33,477 --> 00:00:36,010
Summer!

14
00:00:36,210 --> 00:00:38,143
You always need

15
00:00:38,143 --> 00:00:40,376
a nice dress for a date, right?

16
00:00:40,377 --> 00:00:42,243
So I got one for you.

17
00:00:42,377 --> 00:00:44,410
Look, the size is perfect.

18
00:00:45,543 --> 00:00:48,810
Summer, you're the best, right after

19
00:00:48,810 --> 00:00:50,276
my mom and my boss.

20
00:00:51,643 --> 00:00:53,143
I'll hang it in the best spot

21
00:00:53,143 --> 00:00:54,376
in my closet.

22
00:00:54,743 --> 00:00:56,076
Alright, alright, put it away.

23
00:00:56,377 --> 00:00:58,677
- [Waiter.]
- Coming.

24
00:00:58,843 --> 00:01:00,010
Go on.

25
00:01:31,577 --> 00:01:33,077
What are you sneaking around for?

26
00:01:34,077 --> 00:01:36,443
A bracelet I made using coffee beans.

27
00:01:36,443 --> 00:01:38,076
Look, do you like it?

28
00:01:41,043 --> 00:01:41,843
Hmm.

29
00:01:42,677 --> 00:01:45,077
Just "hmm"? Give it back then.

30
00:01:58,643 --> 00:01:59,543
I like it,

31
00:02:00,443 --> 00:02:01,410
I really like it.

32
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:08,043
[Excuse me.]

33
00:02:13,810 --> 00:02:14,610
[Jia!]

34
00:02:14,677 --> 00:02:19,277
Mr. Lin, I'm really sincere this time.

35
00:02:24,477 --> 00:02:27,443
The guests just left. Go clean up.

36
00:02:28,143 --> 00:02:29,010
Alright.

37
00:02:37,577 --> 00:02:39,143
Say what you need to say.

38
00:02:40,843 --> 00:02:42,810
Do you know her real identity?

39
00:02:43,177 --> 00:02:46,043
[She's Zhu Jinhao, the GM of the Zhu Group]

40
00:02:46,243 --> 00:02:49,076
and in charge of the Aman Island project.

41
00:02:50,643 --> 00:02:51,576
[Take a guess,]

42
00:02:52,410 --> 00:02:55,243
what will happen when she regains memory?

43
00:02:57,543 --> 00:02:59,376
[If she came to talk personally,]

44
00:02:59,743 --> 00:03:00,876
I might consider it.

45
00:03:02,577 --> 00:03:05,210
Lin Qingyi, don't be stubborn.

46
00:03:05,843 --> 00:03:08,876
[Once she remembers, she'll leave you.]

47
00:03:09,477 --> 00:03:10,677
With her skills,

48
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:12,610
